<MethodEndpoint
  method={"delete"}
  path={"/api/users/me/sessions/{sessionId}"}
  context={"endpoint"}
>
  
</MethodEndpoint>



Delete the session of the current user with the given `id` 
and invalidate all tokens related to this session.

You can learn more about sessions [here](../../docs/guides/auth/sessions).

### Tokens
- A valid [`AccessToken`](../../docs/guides/auth/tokens#access-token) is required.
